<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>❤️ For My Love ❤️</title>

<style>
html,body{
margin:0;
padding:0;
font-family:Georgia,serif;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff4d88,#ff99cc,#ff66b2);
color:white;
text-align:center;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

#lock{
position:fixed;
inset:0;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff4d88,#ff66b2,#ff99cc);
z-index:999;
}

#lock input{
padding:12px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
font-size:18px;
text-align:center;
}

#lock button{
margin-top:10px;
padding:10px 25px;
border:none;
border-radius:20px;
cursor:pointer;
font-weight:bold;
color:#ff4d88;
background:white;
}

#main{
display:none;
padding:40px 20px 120px;
}

h1{
font-size:3rem;
animation:pulse 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse{
50%{transform:scale(1.05);}
}

.letter{
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
padding:35px;
border-radius:25px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
line-height:2;
font-size:1.2rem;
box-shadow:0 0 25px rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
}

.heart{
position:fixed;
bottom:-50px;
pointer-events:none;
animation:floatUp linear forwards;
}

@keyframes floatUp{
from{
transform:translateY(0);
opacity:1;
}
to{
transform:translateY(-120vh);
opacity:0;
}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div id="lock">
<h2>❤️ Enter Password ❤️</h2>
<p>Hint: Your special word</p>
<input id="pass" placeholder="Password">
<button onclick="check()">Unlock ❤️</button>
</div>

<div id="main">

<h1>❤️ My Beautiful Girl ❤️</h1>

<div class="letter">

<h2>To The One I Love ❤️</h2>

<p>
I wanted to make something special for you because sometimes words in a text message don't feel big enough for everything I want to say.
</p>

<p>
You mean so much to me. You make ordinary days feel special, and you make me smile even when life gets difficult.
</p>

<p>
When I think about my future, you're the person I want beside me. Not because I have to choose you, but because every day I want to choose you.
</p>

<p>
I love your smile, your voice, your laugh, your personality, and all the little things that make you who you are.
</p>

<p>
I want you to know something important:
</p>

<p>
My loyalty isn't a promise I make because I'm forced to. It's a choice I make because you're the only person I want.
</p>

<p>
I have no interest in looking for someone else. I don't want anyone else. I don't need anyone else.
</p>

<p>
You have my heart completely.
</p>

<p>
I promise to be honest with you, respect you, support you, and stay faithful to you because that's what real love deserves.
</p>

<p>
No matter where life takes us, I want you to remember that you are deeply loved, appreciated, and important to me.
</p>

<p>
Thank you for being you.
</p>

<h3>❤️ Forever Yours ❤️</h3>

</div>

</div>

<script>

function check(){
let p=document.getElementById("pass").value.toLowerCase();

if(p==="yourpassword"){
document.getElementById("lock").style.display="none";
document.getElementById("main").style.display="block";
startHearts();
}
else{
alert("Wrong password ❤️");
}
}

function createHeart(){
let heart=document.createElement("div");

heart.className="heart";
heart.innerHTML="❤️";

heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
heart.style.fontSize=(15+Math.random()*30)+"px";
heart.style.animationDuration=(4+Math.random()*4)+"s";

document.body.appendChild(heart);

setTimeout(()=>{
heart.remove();
},8000);
}

function startHearts(){
setInterval(createHeart,250);
}

</script>

</body>
</html>

